summary: This is a Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) document recording a request to reserve the aircraft registration number 722JH for an entity named HYPERION AIR, with an address in West Palm Beach, FL. The request was made via the FAA Registry's website on October 12, 2020, and a $10 fee was paid.

events.title: Aircraft Registration Reservation Request
events.description: A request was submitted via the FAA Registry's website to reserve the aircraft registration number 722JH for HYPERION AIR.

events.title: Request Acceptance
events.description: The FAA's Civil Aviation Registry accepted the registration reservation request.

keyFacts: The document is an FAA record of a request to reserve the aircraft registration number 722JH.
The request was made on October 12, 2020, by or for an entity named HYPERION AIR.
HYPERION AIR provided an address in West Palm Beach, FL 33406.
A $10 fee was paid for the reservation request, which was accepted by the FAA on December 9, 2020.
